:authenticated:

- list all groups
  -> success
     + list of user's active group ids

- get all groups
  -> success
     + list of user's active groups

- get group
  + list of group ids

  -> success
     + list of group data

- create group
  + group name
  ? group data

  -> success
     + group id
  -> fail

- update group
  + group id
  + group data

- send group join request
  + user
  + group

  -> success
  -> fail

- accept group join request
  + group join request

  -> success
  -> fail

- reject group join request
  + group join request

  -> success
  -> fail

- list of group join requests
  -> success
     + list of active group join requests
     
